quran[30{c,v,t}:
74,18,Innahoo fakkara wa qaddar
74,19,Faqutila kayfa qaddar
74,20,Summa qutila kaifa qaddar
74,21,Summa nazar
74,22,Summa 'abasa wa basar
74,23,Summaa adbara wastakbar
74,24,Faqaala in haazaaa illaa sihruny yu'sar
74,25,In haazaaa illaa qawlul bashar
74,26,Sa usleehi saqar
74,27,Wa maaa adraaka maa saqar
74,28,Laa tubqee wa laa tazar
74,29,Lawwaahatul lilbashar
74,30,'Alaihaa tis'ata 'ashar
74,31,Wa maaja''alnaaa As haaban naari illaa malaaa 'ikatanw wa maa ja'alnaa 'iddatahum illaa fitnatal lillazeena kafaroo liyastayqinal lazeena ootul kitaaba wa yazdaadal lazeena aamanooo eemaananw wa laa yartaabal lazeena ootul kitaaba walmu'minoona wa liyaqoolal lazeena fee quloo bihim maradunw walkaafiroona maazaaa araadal laahu bihaazaa masalaa; kazaalika yudillul laahu many yashaaa'u wa yahdee many yashaaa'; wa maa ya'lamu junooda rabbika illaa hoo; wa maa hiya illaa zikraa lil bashar
74,32,Kallaa walqamar
74,33,Wallaili adbar
74,34,Wassub hi izaaa asfar
74,35,Innahaa la ihdal kubar
74,36,Nazeeral lilbashar
74,37,Liman shaaa'a minkum any yataqaddama aw yata akhkhar
74,38,Kullu nafsim bim kasabat raheenah
74,39,Illaaa as haabal yameen
74,40,Fee jannaatiny yata saaa'aloon
74,41,'Anil mujrimeen
74,42,Maa salakakum fee saqar
74,43,Qaaloo lam naku minal musalleen
74,44,Wa lam naku nut'imul miskeen
74,45,Wa kunnaa nakhoodu ma'al khaaa'ideen
74,46,Wa kunnaa nukazzibu bi yawmid Deen
74,47,Hattaaa ataanal yaqeen
